&lt;li&gt;Identify growth opportunities and translate them into actionable commercial plans with GOV impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and support strategic B2B conversations, business reviews, and negotiations as the Ads &amp;amp; Promos expert&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and motivate a team of high performing account managers in executing high-impact Ad and promo campaigns, ensuring budget discipline, strong performance and Merchant growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including product, marketing, and sales to ensure business objectives are met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connect global and local initiatives and adapt the strategy together with Marketing for our local market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up, manage, and optimize ads and promo campaigns; monitor KPIs and performance using Looker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate data into clear actions and recommendations for local and global stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
